title: Sonny Jurgensen, Pro Football Hall of Fame quarterback, dies at age 91

sources.name: ESPN NFL
sources.title: Hall of Fame quarterback Jurgensen dies at 91
sources.description: Hall of Fame quarterback Sonny Jurgensen, who has held franchise passing records for Philadelphia and Washington for more than five decades, has died at the age of 91.
